com.cyc.session

Interface CycSessionConfiguration.DefaultSessionOptions

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSessionOptionsImpl
    Enclosing interface:
    CycSessionConfiguration

    public static interface CycSessionConfiguration.DefaultSessionOptions
    An immutable set of options, including the name of the cyclist making assertions, and the project's KE purpose. This provides the defaults for the mutable SessionOptions interface.
